Kid Cudi Man on the Moon III: The Chosen (Republic Records) MAN on the Moon III: The Chosen sounds like you are stepping into a new musical world. Kid Cudi’s music takes you on a great experience and people will feel it when listening to this album. He is without a doubt one of the coolest musicians there has ever been. Kid Cudi added some songs on the album about his personal stories and struggles with depression, addiction, loneliness and relationships. Music lovers will enjoy tracks such as Heaven On Earth, The Void, Sad People, Dive and Lord I Know. It also features Phoebe Bridgers, Pop Smoke, Skepta and Trippie Redd. – ANDISWA NGENYANE